               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; incipits or headings of the texts; directives for the celebrants; abbreviations; the words (እሁነ፡) እገሌ፡ and እገሊት፡ standing for the name of the deceased or the baptised; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.&#xD;
&#xD;
The text on fol. 7r is written alternately in red and black lines.</rubric>
